        <MediumExplanationTxt>Form 990-PF, Part XV, Page 11 - Purpose of Grant Paid During the Year.The Friends of the Russian Foundation for Human Reproductive Health disbursed grant funds during fiscal year 2016 to the Russian Foundation for Human Reproductive Health, Maintanance and Recovery for the purpose of developing and operating a training center in Moscow, Russia. The funds are to be used to improve infertility treatment, education, and reproductive assistance in Russia and, specifically, to reconstruct the premises allocated to the training center, provide equipment and supplies to the training center, educate medical personnel, design and produce training materials, provide informational support, and provide financial assistance to patients who cannot pay for the medical care.</MediumExplanationTxt>
